review_blob:
Stink bug fart as I open this, as if infected. Also, that dank stank of boiled hops; settled down after a while with this though. One-dimensional belgian Cat-pee character with some clashing bad hop notes.
Might sound a bit exaggerated, but Not to my tastes at all, Im afraid. Drinkable.
Savory and complex taste. Very citrusy aswell. Drinkable and interesting, recommended.
